{"tid":1825753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥各界對十項惠民政策措施普遍反應正面","createTime":"2020-01-15T14:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T15:31:57.000Z","uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"57318be903e3102bac21d00a5200c7fe7cb8c6c7","tid":1825753,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T14:35:36.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥在社交網站表示，各界對昨天公布的10項惠民政策措施普遍反應正面，最廣受大眾歡迎是讓60到64歲的年長人士，都可以有「2元乘車優惠」，她指出，大多數措施都是制度或政策上的改變，在實行上有很多細節，當局樂意多聽意見。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，期待明天出席立法會答問會，向議員詳細解釋政府的想法及回應他們的提問，又說立法會應該是做實事的地方，希望明天和一直關心民生的議員有良性的互動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503005-20200115.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503005-20200115.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=58d9b6fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503005-20200115.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=913390aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503005-20200115.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"cd61a9b932be59e4e124e4a651bf2374439cb02e","tid":1825753,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T14:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81a36dcdcbf124bf0db3473def722dca4ac5b0e","tid":1825753,"uid":253978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T14:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wQpL99B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwQpL99B.jpg&h=8bd4539e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n119唔出，勇武嘅下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fefc713eeed9be8f0fe8fdbda27de967011b31ac","tid":1825753,"uid":142097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T14:37:24.000Z","msg":"將所有資源比哂廢老"},{"pid":"f376c5